snippet.title: Bridge Deluxe 2 with Omar Sharif gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Bridge Deluxe 2 with Omar Sharif, Dos PC game produced by Interplay in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/omar-sharif-bridge-2/6530/
Bridge Deluxe II with Omar Sharif is another game about the card game of Bridge. The game contains a wide range of options that allow both beginners and experts to enjoy a game of bridge.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
